
Step 1: Download Jenkins : https://www.jenkins.io/download/#downloading-jenkins


Step : Download Docker Hub : https://www.jenkins.io/download/#downloading-jenkins
Step : Download Kubernetes :
Step 1 : Create One spring boot Project.
Step 2 : Create One Test controller and test Application locally.
Step 3 : Create One Github project and push code to github
git init
git add .
git commit -m "first commit"
git status
git branch -M master
git remote add origin git@github.com:Tejas-Yevalkar/cicd-Automation-process-example.git
git push -u origin master

Step 4 : Check code push or not properly

Step 5 : Start Jenkins in browser (http://localhost:8080/)
