Step 6 : Select "New Item" Button and provide your Item Name(Ex: cicd_automation) and select "Pipeline" Option and click "OK" Button

Step 7 : Write Description and Check "GitHub project" and Provide your git Project url.
         In "Build Triggers" part, Select box "GitHub hook trigger for GITScm polling".
         In "Pipeline" Select Definition : "Pipeline Script from SCM"
         SCM : Select GIT and provide your Git URL
         Script Path : Provide Your jenkins file Name and select "Save" Button

Step 8 : In Dashboard select your Pipeline Select build Now.


